  "prompt": "Is there any dual SIM mobile supporting 4G or 4G and 3G?",
  "response": "Yes, many mobile phones support dual SIM functionality with either dual 4G or one SIM supporting 4G and the other supporting 3G. Most modern smartphones from brands like Samsung, Apple, Xiaomi, OnePlus, and others offer dual SIM options with both SIM slots capable of 4G connectivity. Some examples include:\n\n- **Samsung Galaxy series** (e.g., Galaxy S21, S22)\n- **OnePlus series** (e.g., OnePlus 9, 10)\n- **Xiaomi Redmi series** (e.g., Redmi Note 10, Note 11)\n- **Apple iPhone series** (e.g., iPhone 13, 14 with eSIM functionality)\n\nThese phones typically allow users to manage two networks simultaneously, making it easy to balance personal and business usage or local and international plans. Always check the specific model's specifications to ensure it meets your requirements for dual SIM and network support.",
